videos.headline: Marks goes untouched for the opening Mississippi State TD
videos.description: Jo'Quavious Marks gets his first handoff of the game and sprints 28 yards for the Bulldogs' touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Marks goes untouched for the opening Mississippi State TD) 2020/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tulsa, Mississippi State have skirmish before the game
videos.description: There is some pushing and shoving before Tulsa and Mississippi State face off in the Lockheed Martin Armed Forces Bowl.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tulsa, Mississippi State have skirmish before the game) 2020/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Massive postgame brawl erupts between Tulsa, Mississippi State
videos.description: After Mississippi State's win over Tulsa, a violent fight ensued between the two teams.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Massive postgame brawl erupts between Tulsa, Mississippi State) 2020/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Leach reacts to massive brawl after Mississippi State's bowl win
videos.description: Mississippi State coach Mike Leach says he isn't going to lose his mind over the Bulldogs' postgame brawl and adds that his team hasn't had any problems like this during the season.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Leach reacts to massive brawl after Mississippi State's bowl win) 2020/12/31 ESHEET
